  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of KAI-1678 to Treat Pain in Subjects With Postherpetic Neuralgia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo- and Active-Comparator-Controlled, Single-Dose Study to Assess the Efficacy of KAI-1678 Administered by Subcutaneous Infusion in Subjects With Postherpetic Neuralgia</official_title>
