  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of PHN with pain for at least 3 months after segmental herpes zoster
             eruption

          -  pain score at least 4 on 11-point numerical rating scale (0-10)

          -  stable doses of analgesic medications for at least 1 month&quot;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of PHN with pain for at least 3 months after segmental herpes zoster
             eruption

          -  pain score at least 4 on 11-point numerical rating scale (0-10)

          -  stable doses of analgesic medications for at least 1 month&quot;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
